---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SourceLinks from '../components/ui/SourceLinks.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Photography System Specimen — Al-Fananin">
  <style is:global>

        body {
            color: var(--color-text-primary);
            background-color: var(--color-bg-base);
        }

        .en-font {
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            direction: ltr;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .f-amiri {
            font-family: 'Amiri', Georgia, serif;
        }

        .doc-container {
            max-width: 1040px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        section {
            padding: 5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        }

        section:last-of-type {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .section-header {
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .section-num {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            display: block;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .section-desc {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .tag {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: rgba(43, 26, 20, 0.05);
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Abstract Photo Placeholders to avoid generic stock */
        .photo-placeholder {
            background-color: #EEDCB5;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
        }
        
        .photo-placeholder::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
            mix-blend-mode: overlay;
        }
        
        .photo-label {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(43, 26, 20, 0.5);
            border: 1px dashed rgba(43, 26, 20, 0.2);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
        }
    
  </style>



    <header class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
        <div class="doc-container text-center">
            <span class="en-font text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-gray-500 mb-6 block">Art Direction Brief v1.0</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6"><span class="lang-ar">نظام التصوير — ترجمة الضيافة السودانية إلى لغة بصرية قابلة للرغبة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The imaging system—translating Sudanese hospitality into a desirable visual language</span></h1>
            <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto opacity-75 f-amiri leading-relaxed">
                <span class="lang-ar">وثيقة التوجيه الفني لتصوير الأطباق، المشروبات، المساحات، والعناصر البشرية ضمن هوية رقمية راقية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">An artistic direction document for depicting dishes, drinks, spaces, and human elements within a sophisticated digital identity.</span>
                <br><span class="lang-ar">الهدف ليس مجرد توثيق طعام، بل تصوير الملمس (Texture)، الدفء (Warmth)، الكرم (Abundance)، والأصالة (Authenticity).</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The goal is not just to document food, but to capture texture, warmth, generosity, and authenticity.</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- RESEARCH-DRIVEN FOUNDATION -->
        <section class="bg-muted/50 border-b border-subtle py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
                <div class="mb-12 max-w-4xl">
                    <span class="en-text text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-secondary mb-3 block" dir="ltr">Visual Psychology & Conversion</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 f-amiri leading-[1.2]">
                        <span class="lang-ar">سيكولوجية الصورة: <br/><span class="text-red-800">كيف نرفع معدل التحويل البصري؟</span></span>
                        <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Visual Psychology: <br/><span class="text-red-800">How to Boost Visual Conversion?</span></span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-secondary leading-relaxed f-amiri border-r-4 border-red-800/20 pr-6">
                        <span class="lang-ar">تثبت الدراسات أن</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Studies prove that</span> <strong><span class="lang-ar">45% من زوار المواقع يبحثون عن صور الطعام أولاً</span><span class="lang-en hidden">45% of site visitors look for food photos first</span></strong><span class="lang-ar">، وأن الإخراج الفني الاحترافي يرفع نسبة الطلب بـ 30-40%. نظامنا يعتمد القواعد التالية:</span><span class="lang-en hidden">, and professional art direction increases ordering by 30-40%. Our system adopts these rules:</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 border rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2 f-amiri ar-text"><span class="lang-ar">قاعدة الطعام البني (The Brown Rule)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Brown food rule</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-xs opacity-80 leading-relaxed f-amiri ar-text"><span class="lang-ar">المطبخ السوداني غني باليخنات البنية. نستخدم التباين اللوني العالي (العزل على خلفيات فاتحة) لمنع "الفوضى البصرية" وإظهار الجمال العميق للأطباق التقليدية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Sudanese cuisine is rich in brown stews. We use high color contrast (isolating on light backgrounds) to prevent "visual chaos" and show the deep beauty of traditional dishes.</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 border rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2 f-amiri ar-text"><span class="lang-ar">الإضاءة الجانبية (Side-lit Texture)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Side-lit Texture</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-xs opacity-80 leading-relaxed f-amiri ar-text"><span class="lang-ar">الضوء الجانبي (45 درجة) يكشف مسامية الخبز (الكسرة) وتفاصيل اللحوم (الشية). هذا الملمس يولد استجابة عصبية فورية تسمى "الجوع البصري".</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Side-lighting (45 degrees) reveals bread porosity (Kisra) and meat details (Shiya). This texture generates an immediate neural response called "visual hunger".</span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 border rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2 f-amiri ar-text"><span class="lang-ar">المصداقية الاجتماعية (Social Trust)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Social Trust</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-xs opacity-80 leading-relaxed f-amiri ar-text"><span class="lang-ar">الصور التي تشمل عناصر بشرية (يد، صب قهوة) ترفع الثقة بالعلامة التجارية، لأنها تنقل شعور "الضيافة الحية" بدلاً من الصور المعلبة الباردة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Images including human elements (hand, pouring coffee) raise brand trust, as they convey a "living hospitality" feel instead of cold canned photos.</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- DISCLAIMER: RESEARCH CONTEXT -->
        <section class="bg-[#F8F9FA] border-b border-gray-200 py-8">
            <div class="doc-container">
                <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-6 bg-[#EEDCB5]/30 rounded-xl border border-[#D9A92B]/40 text-[#3E2723]">
                    <i data-lucide="info" class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 text-[#9B2226]"></i>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block mb-1 font-bold text-lg"><span class="lang-ar">ملاحظة هامة (توضيح المصدر):</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Important note (clarification of source):</span></strong>
                        <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed opacity-90 f-amiri"><span class="lang-ar">هذا المستند هو</span><span class="lang-en hidden">This document is</span> <strong><span class="lang-ar">نتاج بحث منهجي صارم (Research-Based Brief)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The product of rigorous, systematic research (Research-Based Brief)</span></strong> <span class="lang-ar">تم تصميمه حصرياً استناداً إلى أحدث التوصيات العالمية لخبراء تصوير الأطعمة. الهدف هو تزويدك كخبير فني بالمعايير التي تحقق أعلى معدلات التحويل.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">designed exclusively based on the latest global food photography recommendations. The goal is to provide you as a technical expert with the standards that achieve the highest conversion rates.</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- SECTION 2: ART DIRECTION PHILOSOPHY -->
        <section class="doc-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 2.0</span>
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">فلسفة التوجيه الفني (Art Direction Philosophy)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Art Direction Philosophy</span></h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    <span class="lang-ar">الصور الصاخبة أو المثالية المفرطة تفقد مصداقيتها. التصوير هنا يرفض الأجواء التجارية الاستهلاكية ويتبنى منهجية التوثيق الحميمي. الطعام يبدو وكأنك دعيت إلى وليمة حقيقية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Loud or overly idealized images lose their credibility. Photography here rejects the commercial, consumer atmosphere and adopts the methodology of intimate documentation. The food feels like you've been invited to a real feast.</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="tag mb-3 block w-max">Authenticity</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#9B2226]"><span class="lang-ar">الواقعية الدافئة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Warm realism</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-gray-700"><span class="lang-ar">الابتعاد التام عن إضاءات الفلاش القاسية والصور ذات المظهر البلاستيكي. نعتمد الإضاءة المنتشرة الناعمة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Avoid harsh flash lighting and plastic-looking photos. We adopt soft diffused lighting.</span></p>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="tag mb-3 block w-max">Tactile</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#9B2226]"><span class="lang-ar">الملمس قبل الزخرفة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Texture before decoration</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-gray-700"><span class="lang-ar">يجب أن يشعر المشاهد بمسامية الكسرة وقرمشة الطعمية وسماكة الملاح قبل التركيز على ترتيب زينة الطبق.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The viewer must feel the porosity of the kasra, the crunch of the falafel, and the thickness of the mellah before focusing on the arrangement of the dish’s garnish.</span></p>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="tag mb-3 block w-max">Generosity</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#9B2226]"><span class="lang-ar">الوفرة دون فوضى</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Abundance without clutter</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-gray-700"><span class="lang-ar">تجسيد الكرم السوداني بكثافة الطعام والطبقات، ولكن داخل تكوين هندسي نظيف ومريح للعين.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The embodiment of Sudanese generosity with the density of food and layers, but within a clean geometric composition that is pleasing to the eye.</span></p>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 4 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="tag mb-3 block w-max">Storytelling</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#9B2226]"><span class="lang-ar">الإنسان كجزء من القصة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Man as part of the story</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-gray-700"><span class="lang-ar">يد بشرية تصب القهوة أو تقطع الخبز تضفي حياة وألفة وتلغي الإحساس الاستوديو المعزول.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">A human hand pouring coffee or cutting bread adds life and familiarity and eliminates the isolated studio feel.</span></p>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 5 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="tag mb-3 block w-max">Culture</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#9B2226]"><span class="lang-ar">الهوية السودانية دون استعراض</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Sudanese identity without display</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-gray-700"><span class="lang-ar">استخدام تلميحات ثقافية دقيقة ومندمجة وظيفياً بدلاً من الاستعراض السياحي المبتذل بالأيقونات التقليدية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Using subtle, functionally integrated cultural allusions rather than cheesy tourist display with traditional iconography.</span></p>
                </div>
                <!-- Card 6 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="tag mb-3 block w-max">Conversion</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-[#9B2226]"><span class="lang-ar">الجوع البصري القابل للتحويل</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Transferable visual hunger</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-gray-700"><span class="lang-ar">الهدف النهائي هو الطلب. يجب إبراز اللمعان، العصارة، والتباين اللوني لتحفيز الشهية المباشرة للمشاهد.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The ultimate goal is demand. Luster, juiciness, and color contrast should be highlighted to stimulate the viewer's immediate appetite.</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 3: WHAT THE CAMERA MUST SELL -->
        <section class="bg-[#F8F9FA] border-y border-gray-200">
            <div class="doc-container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 3.0</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">ماذا يجب أن تبيع الكاميرا؟</span><span class="lang-en hidden">What should the camera sell for?</span></h2>
                    <p class="section-desc">
                        <span class="lang-ar">نحن لا نبيع قائمة أطباق (Dish Inventory)، بل نبيع تجربة متكاملة. الكاميرا يجب أن تخترق حاجز الشاشة لتقدم قيماً وظيفية وعاطفية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">We don't sell a menu (Dish Inventory), we sell an integrated experience. The camera must break through the screen barrier to provide functional and emotional values.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="max-w-4xl bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="space-y-6 relative before:absolute before:inset-y-0 before:-right-3 before:w-1 before:bg-gray-100 before:rounded pr-6">
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="absolute -right-[34px] top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#9B2226] flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-white"></div>
                            <strong class="text-xl block text-gray-900 mb-1"><span class="lang-ar">الشهوة الطعامية (The Food Itself)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The Food Itself</span></strong>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="lang-ar">عصارة اللحم، لمعان الزيت، كثافة البخار، ونضارة المكونات.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The juiciness of the meat, the sheen of the oil, the intensity of the steam, and the freshness of the ingredients.</span></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="absolute -right-[34px] top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#E8B730] flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-white"></div>
                            <strong class="text-xl block text-gray-900 mb-1"><span class="lang-ar">المشاركة الجماعية (The Act of Sharing)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The Act of Sharing</span></strong>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="lang-ar">الأيادي الممتدة، التوزيع على أكثر من شخص، ودفء المائدة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The extended hands, the distribution to more than one person, and the warmth of the table.</span></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="absolute -right-[34px] top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#81B29A] flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-white"></div>
                            <strong class="text-xl block text-gray-900 mb-1"><span class="lang-ar">الطقوس الثقافية (Cultural Rituals)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Cultural Rituals</span></strong>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="lang-ar">طريقة صب الجبنة، تقديم الشية على الجمر، وتحضير الكسرة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">How to pour the cheese, serve the shiya on hot coals, and prepare the kasra.</span></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="absolute -right-[34px] top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#3E2723] flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-white"></div>
                            <strong class="text-xl block text-gray-900 mb-1"><span class="lang-ar">جودة المكونات والمصداقية (Trustworthiness)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Ingredient quality and trustworthiness</span></strong>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="lang-ar">وضوح الطبق دون فلاتر ثقيلة لإثبات ثقتنا بجودة ما قدمناه.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The clarity of the dish without heavy filters to prove our confidence in the quality of what we provided.</span></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 4: LIGHTING SYSTEM -->
        <section class="doc-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 4.0</span>
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">عمارة الإضاءة (Lighting System)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Lighting System</span></h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    <span class="lang-ar">الإضاءة هي المُشكل الأساسي للملمس.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Lighting is the primary shaper of texture.</span> <strong><span class="lang-ar">يُمنع تماماً استخدام الفلاش المباشر (Direct Flash)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The use of Direct Flash is strictly prohibited.</span></strong> <span class="lang-ar">أو الإضاءة القاسية التي تعطي الانطباع التجاري الرخيص وتخفي مسامية الأطباق السودانية العميقة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Or the harsh lighting that gives the impression of cheap commercialism and hides the porosity of the deep Sudanese dishes.</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <!-- Lighting Mode 1 -->
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 relative group">
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded shadow-sm text-xs font-bold en-font text-blue-800">Diffused Light</div>
                    <div class="photo-placeholder h-48 mb-4 border border-white/40 shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(120deg, #FDFBF7, #EEDCB5);">
                        <i data-lucide="sun-dim" class="w-12 h-12 text-[#2B1A14] opacity-20 mx-auto mb-2"></i>
                        <span class="photo-label shadow text-center text-xs">Soft Natural Glow</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">الضوء المشتت الناعم</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Soft diffused light</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-80 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-ar">محاكاة ضوء النافذة الشمالية الناعم باستخدام (Softboxes). يقلل حدة الظلال ويعطي إشراقة واقعية طبيعية للطعام.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Simulating the soft light of a northern window using softboxes. Reduces shadows and gives a natural, realistic glow to food.</span></p>
                </div>

                <!-- Lighting Mode 2 -->
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 relative group">
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded shadow-sm text-xs font-bold en-font text-amber-800">Side Light</div>
                    <div class="photo-placeholder h-48 mb-4 border border-white/40 shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #EEDCB5, #cfa86e);">
                        <i data-lucide="flashlight" class="w-12 h-12 text-[#2B1A14] opacity-20 mx-auto mb-2 transform rotate-90"></i>
                        <span class="photo-label shadow text-center text-xs">Texture Reveal</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">الإضاءة الجانبية (45° - 90°)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Side lighting (45° - 90°)</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-80 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-ar">تُلقي بظلال ناعمة وتكشف</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Casts soft shadows and reveals</span> <strong><span class="lang-ar">البنية الطبوغرافية</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Topographic structure</span></strong> <span class="lang-ar">ومسامية وخشونة الأطعمة كالمخبوزات (الكسرة/القراصة) واللحوم المشوية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">And the porosity and roughness of foods such as baked goods (kasra/qarasa) and grilled meat.</span></p>
                </div>

                <!-- Lighting Mode 3 -->
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 relative group">
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded shadow-sm text-xs font-bold en-font text-purple-800">Backlight</div>
                    <div class="photo-placeholder h-48 mb-4 border border-white/40 shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(0deg, #EEDCB5 50%, #ffffff 100%);">
                        <i data-lucide="sun" class="w-12 h-12 text-[#2B1A14] opacity-20 mx-auto mb-2"></i>
                        <span class="photo-label shadow text-center text-xs">Liquid Translucency</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">الإضاءة الخلفية</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Backlight</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-80 leading-relaxed"><span class="lang-ar">مثالية للمشروبات (الكركديه، القهوة)، ولإبراز حواف الأطعمة (Rim Lighting) والتقاط البخار المتصاعد بوضوح عالي.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Ideal for drinks (hibiscus, coffee), highlighting the edges of foods (Rim Lighting) and capturing rising steam with great clarity.</span></p>
                </div>

                <!-- Forbidden Mode -->
                <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-red-300 relative group overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-red-600 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded shadow-sm text-xs font-bold en-font z-20">Direct Flash (Forbidden)</div>
                    <div class="photo-placeholder h-48 mb-4 border border-red-200 shadow-sm relative" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #ffffff 10%, #EEDCB5 90%);">
                        <i data-lucide="zap-off" class="w-12 h-12 text-red-800 opacity-60 mx-auto mb-2 relative z-10"></i>
                         <!-- Harsh simulated shadow -->
                        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-24 h-5 bg-black/60 transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 blur-[2px] rounded-full z-0"></div>
                        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-20 h-20 bg-white shadow-xl transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border border-gray-300 z-10"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 text-red-800 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">الفلاش המباشر (مرفوض)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Flash started (rejected)</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-red-900"><span class="lang-ar">يُسطح عمق الطبق، يولد انعكاسات متوهجة ومزعجة على الزيوت والمرق، ويخلق ظلالاً سوداء قاسية ومشوهة خلف المكونات.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">It flattens the depth of the dish, generates annoying glowing reflections on oils and broths, and creates harsh, distorted black shadows behind ingredients.</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 5: CAMERA ANGLES BY DISH GEOMETRY -->
        <section class="bg-[#2B1A14] text-white py-24">
            <div class="doc-container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num en-font text-gray-400">SECTION 5.0</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">هندسة الطبق وزوايا الكاميرا</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Dish geometry and camera angles</span></h2>
                    <p class="section-desc opacity-70">
                        <span class="lang-ar">الزاوية تتبع هندسة الطبق والقصة المراد سردها. لا تُصور جميع المكتوبات من زاوية واحدة. زاوية الكاميرا أداة لتوجيه عين الزائر للمعلومة الغذائية الأهم.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The angle follows the geometry of the dish and the story to be told. Not all writings are depicted from one angle. The camera angle is a tool to direct the visitor's eye to the most important nutritional information.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <!-- Angle 1 -->
                    <div class="border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 relative">
                        <span class="en-font font-bold text-xs bg-white/10 px-2 py-1 rounded absolute top-4 left-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Overhead / Flat-lay</span>
                        <div class="h-40 mt-8 mb-6 border border-white/20 rounded bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center relative">
                            <!-- Graphical representation of an overhead shot -->
                            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border-4 border-dashed border-[#F4A261] opacity-60"></div>
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-[#81B29A] absolute top-4 right-4 opacity-50"></div>
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded border-2 border-white/40 absolute bottom-4 left-6 opacity-40"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-[#F4A261]"><span class="lang-ar">الزاوية العلوية (90°)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Top angle (90°)</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed mb-4"><span class="lang-ar">مثالية لاستعراض المائدة الممتلئة، لـ "الصينية السودانية" التشاركية، المخبوزات والأطباق المسطحة. تبرز الوفرة (Abundance) والهياكل التنظيمية للوجبة والترتيب الجمالي لعناصر المائدة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Perfect for showcasing a full table, for sharing 'Sudanese tray', baked goods and flat dishes. Abundance, the organizational structures of the meal, and the aesthetic arrangement of table items stand out.</span></p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Angle 2 -->
                    <div class="border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 relative">
                        <span class="en-font font-bold text-xs bg-white/10 px-2 py-1 rounded absolute top-4 left-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Diner’s View / 45°</span>
                        <div class="h-40 mt-8 mb-6 border border-white/20 rounded bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center relative perspective-container">
                             <!-- Graphical representation of a 45 degree shot -->
                             <div class="w-32 h-12 bg-[#81B29A]/30 rounded-[50%] absolute top-1/2 mt-4 transform -translate-y-1/2 scale-y-50 blur-[2px]"></div>
                             <div class="w-28 h-10 border-b-4 border-l-4 border-solid border-white/60 rounded-[50%] absolute top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 scale-y-50 mb-2"></div>
                             <div class="w-24 h-6 border bg-[#F4A261]/80 rounded-[50%] absolute top-[35%] transform scale-y-50"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-[#81B29A]"><span class="lang-ar">زاوية نظر الجالس (45°)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Sitting angle of view (45°)</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed mb-4"><span class="lang-ar">زاوية الرؤية الطبيعية للضيف عند جلوسه. الأفضل لتصوير الأعماق القليلة مثل أطباق (الملاح) واليخنات العميقة. تخلق تواصلاً نفسياً ودعوة استباقية للتذوق المباشر.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The natural viewing angle of the guest when sitting. Best for shooting shallow depths such as malah dishes and deep stews. Creates a psychological connection and a proactive invitation to direct tasting.</span></p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Angle 3 -->
                    <div class="border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 relative">
                        <span class="en-font font-bold text-xs bg-white/10 px-2 py-1 rounded absolute top-4 left-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Side Profile / 0°</span>
                        <div class="h-40 mt-8 mb-6 border border-white/20 rounded bg-white/5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1">
                             <!-- Graphical representation of a side profile shot -->
                             <div class="w-20 h-4 bg-orange-200/50 rounded-full"></div>
                             <div class="w-22 h-3 bg-red-800/60 rounded"></div>
                             <div class="w-20 h-4 bg-orange-300/40 rounded-full mt-1"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-white/90"><span class="lang-ar">زاوية الصفر والأفق (0°)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Zero angle and horizon (0°)</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed mb-4"><span class="lang-ar">الزاوية الجانبية الموازية للطاولة. مثالية للكشف عن تكوين الطبقات (Layers) لساندويتش أو برجر، ولإبراز الارتفاع للأكواب الطويلة وتعرجات السوائل أو المشروبات المصبوبة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The side corner parallel to the table. Ideal for revealing the layered composition of a sandwich or burger, and for highlighting the height of tall cups and slushies of poured liquids or drinks.</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 6: THE BROWN FOOD RULE -->
        <section class="bg-[#F8F9FA] border-y border-gray-200">
            <div class="doc-container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 6.0</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title text-[#780000]"><span class="lang-ar">قاعدة الأطعمة البنية (The "Brown Food" Rule)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The "Brown Food" Rule</span></h2>
                    <p class="section-desc">
                        <span class="lang-ar">المعضلة الكبرى: المطبخ السوداني غني جداً باليخنات واللحوم ذات الألوان الداكنة أو الترابية (شية، فول، تقلية) التي تميل للون "البني". هذه الأطعمة إذا لم تُصور بذكاء ستبدو مسطحة وباهتة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The biggest dilemma: Sudanese cuisine is very rich in stews and meats that are dark or earthy in color (shia, fava beans, taqliyya), which tend to be “brown.” If these foods are not photographed intelligently, they will look flat and dull.</span> <strong><span class="lang-ar">هنا نطبق قوانين التباين الصارمة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Here we apply strict laws of contrast.</span></strong>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-[#780000] flex items-center gap-2">
                                <i data-lucide="triangle-alert" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                                <span class="lang-ar">قوانين المواجهة للفوضى البصرية البنية</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Laws of confrontation for brown visual chaos</span>
                            </h3>
                            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm opacity-90 text-gray-800 f-amiri text-lg">
                                <li class="border-b pb-2"><strong><span class="lang-ar">حتمية التزيين الدقيقة (Garnish is Mandatory):</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Garnish is Mandatory:</span></strong> <span class="lang-ar">يُمنع تصوير أي طبق بني أو داكن عميق بدون إضافة بُعد لوني مغاير يكسر الرتابة بطريقة عضوية.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">It is forbidden to photograph any deep brown or dark dish without adding a contrasting color dimension that breaks the monotony in an organic way.</span></li>
                                <li class="border-b pb-2"><strong><span class="lang-ar">لمعة العصارة (Oil Sheen):</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Oil Sheen:</span></strong> <span class="lang-ar">إبراز قطرات الزيت أو السمن بدقة عالية من خلال "الضوء الجانبي" لمنع الطبق من الظهور جافاً.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Highlighting drops of oil or ghee with high precision through the “side light” to prevent the dish from appearing dry.</span></li>
                                <li class="border-b pb-2"><strong><span class="lang-ar">عزل الخلفية الفاتحة (Light Plates):</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Isolating the light background (Light Plates):</span></strong> <span class="lang-ar">تقديم الأطباق الداكنة بداخل فخار أو خزف فاتح اللون/أبيض لعزل الطعام بصرياً كـ "بطل للصورة" لعدم ضياع ملامحه.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Serving dark dishes inside light/white pottery or porcelain to visually isolate the food as a “photo hero” so as not to lose its features.</span></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Mini Do / Don't block specifically for brown foods -->
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <!-- Bad Example Mock -->
                            <div class="border-2 border-red-200 bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
                               <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#5D4037] flex-shrink-0 grid place-items-center opacity-80 border-2 border-[#3E2723]"></div>
                               <div>
                                   <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                                       <span class="bg-red-200 text-red-800 text-[10px] en-font font-bold px-1 rounded uppercase">Avoid</span>
                                       <span class="font-bold text-red-900 text-sm"><span class="lang-ar">تباين ضعيف (Muddy)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Low contrast (Muddy)</span></span>
                                   </div>
                                   <p class="text-xs opacity-70"><span class="lang-ar">طبق غامق، إضاءة مسطحة، لون موحد بلا ملامح واضحة. يبدو غير شهي إطلاقاً.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Dark dish, flat lighting, uniform color with no clear features. It looks completely unappetizing.</span></p>
                               </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Good Example Mock -->
                            <div class="border-2 border-green-200 bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4 relative overflow-hidden">
                               <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 w-8 bg-gradient-to-l from-white/40 to-transparent"></div>
                               <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white flex-shrink-0 grid place-items-center shadow-md relative">
                                   <!-- Plate content simulated -->
                                   <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#5D4037] shadow-inner relative overflow-hidden">
                                       <div class="absolute top-2 right-2 w-3 h-3 bg-white/60 rounded-full blur-[1px]"></div> <!-- Highlight -->
                                       <div class="absolute -bottom-1 -left-1 w-6 h-4 bg-green-500/80 rounded blur-[2px]"></div> <!-- Herb Garnish -->
                                   </div>
                               </div>
                               <div>
                                   <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                                       <span class="bg-green-200 text-green-800 text-[10px] en-font font-bold px-1 rounded uppercase">Enforced</span>
                                       <span class="font-bold text-green-900 text-sm"><span class="lang-ar">تباين مقنع (Optimized)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Optimized contrast</span></span>
                                   </div>
                                   <p class="text-xs opacity-70"><span class="lang-ar">استخدام الطبق الفاتح. إضاءة جانبية تكشف اللمعة، ولمسات خضراء طازجة (زينة الكزبرة) تكسر الجمود البصري.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Use a light dish. Side lighting reveals the shine, and fresh green touches (coriander garnish) break the visual deadness.</span></p>
                               </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 7: STYLING AND GARNISH RULES -->
        <section class="doc-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 7.0</span>
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="lang-ar">قواعد التزيين والتنسيق (Styling & Garnish)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Styling & Garnish rules</span></h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    <span class="lang-ar">الزينة ليست مجرد لون يوضع بخلاف سياق الطبق. التزين أداة عضوية تُوظّف لإضاءة التصميم، لخلق تباين متوازن، ولتصريح مصداقية مكونات الأكلة دون خداع بصري أو ابتذال تجاري.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">A garnish is not just a color placed outside of the context of a dish. Garnish is an organic tool used to illuminate a design, create balanced contrast, and convey the authenticity of a food's ingredients without optical illusion or commercial vulgarity.</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                    <span class="en-font text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 mb-2 block tracking-wider">HERBS</span>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full border border-green-200 mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i data-lucide="leaf" class="text-green-700 w-5 h-5"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">أعشاب ونضارة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Herbs and freshness</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-70"><span class="lang-ar">إيحاء بالطراوة الفورية، تكسر صلابة الأطعمة البنية وتضيف حيوية خضراء (كزبرة، شبت).</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Insinuating instant softness, it breaks the toughness of brown foods and adds green vitality (coriander, dill).</span></p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                    <span class="en-font text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 mb-2 block tracking-wider">CHILI / SPICES</span>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full border border-red-200 mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i data-lucide="flame" class="text-red-700 w-5 h-5"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">بهارات حادة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Sharp spices</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-70"><span class="lang-ar">نقاط حمراء كفلفل أو توابل لإضفاء لمسة بصرية تتعدى الشكل إلى نقل إحساس الحرارة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Red dots, such as pepper or spices, add a visual touch that goes beyond form to convey a sense of heat.</span></p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                    <span class="en-font text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 mb-2 block tracking-wider">TEXTURE</span>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#EEDCB5] rounded-full border border-[#D9A92B] mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i data-lucide="grip" class="text-[#9B2226] w-5 h-5"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">حبيبات وقرمشة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Granules and crunch</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-70"><span class="lang-ar">ذرات السمسم، والمكسرات، والكسرات السطحية لتوكيد السطح العضوي وقوامه الهندسي.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Sesame atoms, nuts, and surface crumbs to emphasize the organic surface and its geometric texture.</span></p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                    <span class="en-font text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 mb-2 block tracking-wider">MESS</span>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 rounded-full border border-gray-300 mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i data-lucide="lasso" class="text-gray-700 w-5 h-5"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2"><span class="lang-ar">آثار التقديم</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Submission effects</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-70"><span class="lang-ar">آثار الشواء والفحم وأطراف الطبق غير النمطية كإثبات موثوق لرحلة تحضير الطعام الطازجة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Grill traces, charcoal and atypical plate edges as reliable proof of the fresh food preparation journey.</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 8: STORYTELLING & HUMAN ELEMENT -->
        <section class="doc-container border-t pt-16 mt-16">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-num en-font">SECTION 8.0</span>
                <h2 class="section-title text-[#9B2226]"><span class="lang-ar">عنصر الإنسان والسرد القصصي</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The human element and storytelling</span></h2>
                <p class="section-desc">
                    <span class="lang-ar">الصورة الخالية من أثر بشري قد تبدو معقمة وكئيبة كصور القوائم الطبية. الصور ذات الإخراج السردي هي ما يكسر حاجز الشاشة، وتنقل تجربة كاملة للمشاهد، وتبرز الهوية الحقيقية في التفاصيل الصغيرة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">An image devoid of human traces may appear as sterile and depressing as medical menu images. Images with narrative direction are what break the screen barrier, convey a complete experience to the viewer, and highlight the true identity in the small details.</span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="photo-placeholder h-80 rounded-2xl border-none shadow-xl bg-gray-900 group">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547592180-85f173990554?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 mix-blend-overlay group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500" alt="Narrative Food Photography Context">
                    <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 left-6 text-white text-right">
                        <span class="en-font bg-white/20 px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded backdrop-blur inline-block mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Human Connection</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl drop-shadow-md"><span class="lang-ar">اللمسة البشرية الدافئة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The warm human touch</span></h4>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-lg f-amiri leading-relaxed opacity-90 border-r-4 border-[#9B2226] pr-4 bg-red-50/50 p-4 rounded-l">
                        <span class="lang-ar">"المثالية العيادية الصارمة عدوة الجاذبية". اترك بضع قطرات صلصة عشوائية طفيفة ونتوءات غير مرتبة. فهذه "النواقص" تنبض بالحياة وتشجع العين والمخ على تقبل التجربة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">“Strict clinical idealism is the enemy of gravity.” Leave a few slight random sauce drops and messy bumps. These “shortcomings” come alive and encourage the eye and brain to accept the experience.</span>
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <i data-lucide="hand" class="text-[#E8B730] w-6 h-6 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="block"><span class="lang-ar">أيدي تتحرك في الكادر</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Hands moving in the frame</span></strong>
                                <span class="text-sm opacity-70"><span class="lang-ar">يد تقطع كسرة أو تمرر شية بانسجام. تُضفي سياقاً حميمياً وتثبت كرم التشارك والإيقاع الاجتماعي.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">A hand cuts a crumb or passes a piece of paper in unison. It adds an intimate context and establishes the generosity of sharing and social rhythm.</span></span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <i data-lucide="cookie" class="text-[#E8B730] w-6 h-6 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                            <div>
