                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-[#F4A261]"><span class="lang-ar">3. العلامات الغذائية السريعة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">3. Quick nutritional labels</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-60 leading-relaxed text-white/70"><span class="lang-ar">علامات إرشادية صغيرة ترافق قوائم الطعام تُشير إلى المتطلبات الغذائية (نباتي، حار جداً، مسببات حساسية) وتلعب دور العلامات التحذيرية الخاطفة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Small signposts accompanying menus indicate dietary requirements (vegetarian, extra spicy, allergens) and act as warning signs.</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION 11 & 14 (Geometry) -->
            <section class="mb-20">
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <span class="en-mono text-[10px] text-[#F4A261] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] block mb-2">SECTION 11.0 & 14.0</span>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-black f-amiri text-white mb-4"><span class="lang-ar">التشكيل الهندسي والاتساق البصري</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Geometric composition and visual consistency</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-lg opacity-70 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl text-white/80">
                        <span class="lang-ar">لتجنب أي "ضوضاء بصرية"، تخضع جميع الأيقونات لقوانين هندسية صارمة جداً تتعلق بسُمك الخط الحواف لتظهر وكأنها رُسمت بيد شخص واحد وفي نفس اللحظة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">To avoid any "visual noise", all icons are subject to very strict geometric rules regarding the thickness of the line edges to appear as if they were drawn by one person at the same time.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-green-500 mt-1"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
                            <div>
                                <span class="font-bold block text-lg text-white mb-1"><span class="lang-ar">النمط الخطي المتفرغ (Outline Icons)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Outline icons</span></span>
                                <p class="text-sm opacity-60 text-white/70"><span class="lang-ar">عدم استخدام الأيقونات الممتلئة (Solid/Filled) لضمان الخفة والحداثة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Do not use solid/filled icons to ensure lightness and modernity.</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-green-500 mt-1"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
                            <div>
                                <span class="font-bold block text-lg text-white mb-1"><span class="lang-ar">السمك الموحد (Stroke Width = 2px)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Uniform thickness (Stroke Width = 2px)</span></span>
                                <p class="text-sm opacity-60 text-white/70"><span class="lang-ar">قانون ثابت غير قابل للكسر، إلا عند تغيير حجم الأيقونة لنسب ضخمة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Fixed, unbreakable rule, except when resizing the icon to huge proportions.</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-green-500 mt-1"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
                            <div>
                                <span class="font-bold block text-lg text-white mb-1"><span class="lang-ar">النهايات الدائرية (Round Caps & Joins)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Round Caps & Joins</span></span>
                                <p class="text-sm opacity-60 text-white/70"><span class="lang-ar">جميع حواف وتقاطعات خطوط الأيقونة تكون دائرية ليعكس الطابع العضوي والودود.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">All edges and intersections of the icon's lines are rounded to reflect an organic and friendly feel.</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
                        <p class="text-center font-bold opacity-40 mb-8 text-xs en-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60">Functional Specimen (Lucide)</p>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 h-28 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3 text-white/80 group hover:bg-[#F4A261]/10 hover:border-[#F4A261]/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="search" stroke-width="2" class="w-6 h-6"></i><span class="en-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">Search</span></div>
                            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 h-28 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3 text-white/80 group hover:bg-[#F4A261]/10 hover:border-[#F4A261]/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="menu" stroke-width="2" class="w-6 h-6"></i><span class="en-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">Menu</span></div>
                            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 h-28 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3 text-white/80 group hover:bg-[#F4A261]/10 hover:border-[#F4A261]/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="map-pin" stroke-width="2" class="w-6 h-6"></i><span class="en-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">Location</span></div>
                            
                            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 h-28 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3 text-white/80 group hover:bg-[#F4A261]/10 hover:border-[#F4A261]/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="chevron-left" stroke-width="2" class="w-6 h-6"></i><span class="en-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">Arrow</span></div>
                            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 h-28 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3 text-white/80 group hover:bg-[#F4A261]/10 hover:border-[#F4A261]/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="clock" stroke-width="2" class="w-6 h-6"></i><span class="en-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">Clock</span></div>
                            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 h-28 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3 text-white/80 group hover:bg-[#F4A261]/10 hover:border-[#F4A261]/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="utensils" stroke-width="2" class="w-6 h-6"></i><span class="en-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">Dining</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION 15 & 16 -->
            <section class="mb-20">
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <span class="en-mono text-[10px] text-[#F4A261] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] block mb-2">SECTION 15.0 & 16.0</span>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-black f-amiri text-white mb-4"><span class="lang-ar">التلوين الديناميكي والتفاعل العاطفي</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Dynamic coloring and emotional interaction</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-lg opacity-70 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl text-white/80">
                        <span class="lang-ar">تصميم الأيقونات التفاعلية يجب أن يخدم وظيفتين: إيصال وضوح هيكلي لوني، وابتكار مشاعر وانطباعات محلية متصلة بالذاكرة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Interactive icon design should serve two functions: conveying structural and color clarity, and creating local, memorable feelings and impressions.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                    <!-- Color Rules -->
                    <div class="p-8 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-white border-b border-white/10 pb-4"><span class="lang-ar">وراثة الألوان (currentColor)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Inheriting colors (currentColor)</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-white/80 mb-8">
                            <span class="lang-ar">ممنوع تماماً ترميز ألوان ثابتة داخل عقدة الـ SVG. يجب أن ترث جميع الأيقونات لون الحاوية الأب عبر خاصية</span><span class="lang-en hidden">It is strictly forbidden to encode fixed colors inside an SVG node. All icons must inherit the color of the parent container via a property</span> <code class="en-mono bg-white/10 px-2 py-1 rounded text-[#F4A261]">currentColor</code> <span class="lang-ar">لتتفاعل بسلاسة مع حالات التفعيل (Hover/Active) وتبديل النُسق المبسط.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">To interact seamlessly with Hover/Active states and simplified theme switching.</span>
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="bg-white/5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 rounded-xl text-white/30 border border-white/5"><i data-lucide="heart"></i><span class="text-[9px] mt-4 opacity-40 en-mono uppercase">Default</span></div>
                            <div class="bg-teal-500/10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 rounded-xl text-teal-500 border border-teal-500/30"><i data-lucide="heart" class="fill-current"></i><span class="text-[9px] mt-4 en-mono uppercase">Active</span></div>
                            <div class="bg-red-500/10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 rounded-xl text-red-500 border border-red-500/30"><i data-lucide="info"></i><span class="text-[9px] mt-4 en-mono uppercase">Semantic</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Cultural Interaction (Siniya) -->
                    <div class="p-8 border border-[#F4A261]/20 rounded-2xl bg-[#F4A261]/5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 0%, #F4A261 0%, transparent 50%);"></div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-[#F4A261] border-b border-[#F4A261]/20 pb-4 relative z-10"><span class="lang-ar">استبدال الـ (Cart) بمفهوم (الصينية)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Replacing "Cart" with the concept of "Siniya" (Sudanese Tray)</span></h4>
                        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed text-white/90 mb-8 relative z-10">
                            <span class="lang-ar">التقليل من مصطلحات التسوق الإلكتوني الجامدة ("Add to Cart") وربطها بالتجربة والضيافة. تفاعل الإضافة للطلبات يتحول لرسوم متحركة (Micro-interaction) حيث تنزل الأطباق بصرياً نحو "الصينية"، مما يعزز ردود الفعل العاطفية (Emotional Feedback) ويرسخ تموضع العلامة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Reducing the rigid terms of online shopping (“Add to Cart”) and linking them to the experience and hospitality. Addition interaction for orders turns into a micro-interaction as the dishes visually descend towards the tray, enhancing emotional feedback and solidifying the brand's positioning.</span>
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative z-10 py-4">
                            <!-- Large Circular Siniya Visualization -->
                            <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#E5E7EB] via-[#9CA3AF] to-[#4B5563] shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden border-4 border-[#D1D5DB]/30 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500">
                                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_30%,rgba(255,255,255,0.4),transparent)]"></div>
                                <div class="w-[85%] h-[85%] rounded-full border-2 border-white/10 shadow-inner"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION 17 -->
            <section class="mb-12">
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <span class="en-mono text-[10px] text-[#F4A261] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] block mb-2">SECTION 17.0</span>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-black f-amiri text-white mb-4"><span class="lang-ar">قانون المرايا للمحتوى العربي (RTL Mirroring Law)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Mirror Law for Arabic Content (RTL Mirroring Law)</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-lg opacity-70 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl text-white/80">
                        <span class="lang-ar">لأن التطبيق يدعم الواجهة العربية (من اليمين لليسار) والإنجليزية، فإن مجرد محاذاة النص ليست كافية. يتوجب على واجهة المستخدم عكس (Mirror) أي أيقونة تدل على اتجاه حركي أو تسارعي. عدم الالتزام بذلك يكسر الإدراك التوجيهي للمستخدم العربي.</span>
                        <span class="lang-en hidden">Because the application supports Arabic (right to left) and English interface, simply aligning the text is not enough. The user interface must mirror any icon that indicates a direction of movement or acceleration. Failure to adhere to this breaks the Arab user's orientation awareness.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 bg-white/5 border-b border-white/10">
                        <div class="p-6 text-[#F4A261] font-bold text-center border-r border-white/10"><span class="lang-ar">أيقونات يُمنع عكسها (Do NOT Mirror)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Do NOT Mirror icons</span></div>
                        <div class="p-6 text-teal-400 font-bold text-center"><span class="lang-ar">أيقونات إجبارية العكس (MUST Mirror)</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Mandatory Mirror icons (MUST Mirror)</span></div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 divide-x divide-white/10 h-full">
                        <!-- Non directional -->
                        <div class="p-8 space-y-8">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
                                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 text-white/70 group-hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="search" class="w-6 h-6"></i></div>
                                <div><strong class="block text-white text-lg"><span class="lang-ar">أيقونة البحث</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Search icon</span></strong><p class="opacity-40 text-xs text-white/60"><span class="lang-ar">شكل العدسة الزجاجية عالمي.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">The glass lens shape is universal.</span></p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
                                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 text-white/70 group-hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="clock" class="w-6 h-6"></i></div>
                                <div><strong class="block text-white text-lg"><span class="lang-ar">عقارب الساعة</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Clockwise</span></strong><p class="opacity-40 text-xs text-white/60"><span class="lang-ar">دوران الزمن قياسي وغير مرتبط باللغة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Clock rotation is standard and not language-bound.</span></p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
                                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 text-white/70 group-hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-6 h-6"></i></div>
                                <div><strong class="block text-white text-lg"><span class="lang-ar">علامات التأكيد</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Confirmation signs</span></strong><p class="opacity-40 text-xs text-white/60"><span class="lang-ar">صح أو خطأ علامات دولية مجردة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">True/false are universal abstract marks.</span></p></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Directional -->
                        <div class="p-8 space-y-8 bg-teal-500/5">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
                                <div class="relative">
                                    <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-teal-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-teal-500/30 text-teal-400 transform rotate-180 transition-transform shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6"></i></div>
                                </div>
                                <div><strong class="block text-white text-lg"><span class="lang-ar">الأسهم التوجيهية</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Guiding arrows</span></strong><p class="opacity-40 text-xs text-white/60"><span class="lang-ar">المستقبل والتقدم في اللغة العربية نحو اليسار.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Future and progress in Arabic flow to the left.</span></p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
                                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-teal-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-teal-500/30 text-teal-400 transform rotate-180 shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="log-out" class="w-6 h-6"></i></div>
                                <div><strong class="block text-white text-lg"><span class="lang-ar">أيقونات الخروج/الدخول</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Logout/login icons</span></strong><p class="opacity-40 text-xs text-white/60"><span class="lang-ar">دائماً ما تعكس حركة النص وتدفقه.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Always reflects the direction of text flow.</span></p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
                                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-teal-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-teal-500/30 text-teal-400 transform scale-x-[-1] shadow-lg"><i data-lucide="refresh-cw" class="w-6 h-6"></i></div>
                                <div><strong class="block text-white text-lg"><span class="lang-ar">أيقونات التحديث</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Refresh icons</span></strong><p class="opacity-40 text-xs text-white/60"><span class="lang-ar">الدوران يتبع اتجاه حركة العين واللغة.</span><span class="lang-en hidden">Rotation follows eye and language movement.</span></p></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </section>

